children.subject: would you consider taking 161 as opposed to 188? I believe that's also open this summer. I haven't taken 188 so I'm not sure how it compares but 161 is not too heavy.

history.content: Hi! Just wanted to know what other people's opinions were on taking CS169 & CS188 together this summer? I know it's suggested that people take one tech but I've heard that both classes individually are relatively doable. I've taken summer classes before (61b + a breadth last summer) so I know how fast summer pace can be. Would it be better to take 3 tech during my senior spring (CS61C, another CS upper div, and one of these two classes)?
history.subject: CS169 & CS188 Over Summer?
